Kind: captions
Language: sw

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Clarence Bitegeko
Reviewer: Nelson Simfukwe

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:15.121
Kupata elimu ya chuo

00:00:15.145 --> 00:00:17.300
ni uwekezaji wa miaka 20

00:00:18.220 --> 00:00:19.875
Unapokulia katika umaskini,

00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:22.836
unakuwa hujazoea 
kufikiria mbele kiasi hicho

00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:26.006
Badala yake, 
unafikiria wapi utapata mlo unaofuata

00:00:26.010 --> 00:00:29.076
na namna gani familia yako 
italipa kodi ya pango kwa mwezi huo

00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:32.236
Mbali na hilo, 
wazazi wangu na wazazi wa rafiki zangu

00:00:32.260 --> 00:00:36.660
walionekana kuwa vizuri tu wakiendesha 
teksi na kufanya kazi za usafi na uhudumu.

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:38.636
Ni mpaka nilipokuwa kijana

00:00:38.660 --> 00:00:41.140
nilipogundua sikutaka kufanya kazi zile.

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:45.556
Wakati huo, nilikuwa theluthi mbili 
ya muda wa kumaliza elimu yangu

00:00:45.580 --> 00:00:48.340
na ilikuwa bado kidogo tu 
ningechelewa kufanya mabadiliko.

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:51.660
Unapokulia umaskini, unataka kuwa tajiri.

00:00:52.620 --> 00:00:53.820
Sikuwa tofauti

00:00:54.420 --> 00:00:56.156
Mi ni wa pili kuzaliwa kati ya saba,

00:00:56.180 --> 00:00:58.596
na nililelewa na mama pekee 
kwa msaada wa serikali

00:00:58.620 --> 00:00:59.820
mjini Queens, New York.

00:01:00.310 --> 00:01:02.496
Kwa sababu ya kukulia 
kwenye kipato cha chini,

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:03.930
mimi na ndugu zangu tulikwenda

00:01:03.930 --> 00:01:07.310
kwenye baadhi ya shule za umma 
zilizo duni sana katika Jiji la New York

00:01:07.310 --> 00:01:10.220
Nilikosa shule zaidi ya mara 60 
nilipokuwa darasa la 7

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:13.100
kwa sababu sikujisikia kwenda darasani.

00:01:13.700 --> 00:01:16.756
Katika shule yangu ya sekondari, 
kwa wastani ni 55% walihitimu

00:01:16.779 --> 00:01:18.076
na kibaya zaidi,

00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:20.396
ni 20% tu ya waliohitimu

00:01:20.420 --> 00:01:21.620
walikuwa tayari kwa chuo.

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:24.840
Nilipoingia chuo,

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:26.376
nilimwambia rafiki yangu Brennan

00:01:26.380 --> 00:01:30.076
jinsi gani walimu wetu 
walituambia tunyooshe mikono juu

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:32.100
kama tulitaka kwenda chuo.

00:01:33.220 --> 00:01:34.976
Nilishtushwa pale Brennan aliposema,

00:01:34.980 --> 00:01:37.660
"Karim, 
sijawahi kuulizwa swali hilo kabla."

00:01:38.540 --> 00:01:41.516
Daima lilikuwa, "Ni chuo gani unakwenda?"

00:01:41.540 --> 00:01:43.476
Namna tu swali lilivyoulizwa

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:46.500
ilifanya kuwa jambo lisiliokubalika 
kwa yeye kutokwenda chuo.

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:49.820
Sikuhizi naulizwa swali tofauti.

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:52.780
"Uliwezaje kufanikiwa kutoka?"

00:01:53.580 --> 00:01:55.940
Kwa miaka nilisema nilikuwa na bahati,

00:01:57.140 --> 00:01:58.340
Lakini haikuwa bahati tu.

00:01:59.100 --> 00:02:01.676
Mimi na kaka yangu mkubwa 
tulipomaliza sekondari

00:02:01.700 --> 00:02:02.956
katika wakati mmoja

00:02:02.980 --> 00:02:05.196
na baadaye akaacha chuo 
chuo cha miaka miwili

00:02:05.220 --> 00:02:07.676
Nilitaka kujua kwanini aliacha

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:08.900
na niliendelea kusoma

00:02:10.060 --> 00:02:13.436
Ni mpaka nilipofika Cornell 
kama Mwafunzi wa Utafiti wa Kirais

00:02:13.460 --> 00:02:17.196
ndipo nilipoanza kujifunza 
juu ya matokeo halisi ya kielimu

00:02:17.220 --> 00:02:19.995
yatokanayo na malezi ya mama pekee 
kwa msaada wa serikali

00:02:20.019 --> 00:02:21.820
na kusoma shule nilizosoma.

00:02:22.739 --> 00:02:26.580
Pale ndipo njia ya kaka yangu mkubwa 
ilipoanza kuleta maana kamili kwangu.

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:31.476
Nilijifunza pia kuwa 
wanamaboresho elimu wetu maarufu

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:35.156
watu kama Arne Duncan, 
Waziri wa zamani wa Elimu Marekani

00:02:35.180 --> 00:02:37.876
au Wendy Kopp, 
mwanzilishi wa Teach For America,

00:02:37.900 --> 00:02:41.330
hawajawahi kusoma kwenye shule za umma
za ndani ndani ya jiji kama mimi.

00:02:41.340 --> 00:02:45.156
Kwa hiyo maboresho mengi ya elimu 
yanaendeshwa na mtazamo wa kihuruma

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:46.436
ambapo watu wanasema

00:02:46.460 --> 00:02:49.476
"Twende tukasaidie hawa watoto maskini 
wa ndani ndani ya jiji

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:51.500
au hawa watoto maskini weusi na wakilatino

00:02:52.140 --> 00:02:54.516
badala ya mtazamo wa uelewa,

00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:57.956
ambapo mtu ka' mimi, aliyekulia
katika mazingira haya, ningeweza kusema,

00:02:57.980 --> 00:03:00.196
"Najua taabu mnazokumbana nazo

00:03:00.220 --> 00:03:02.060
na ninataka kuwasaidia kuzishinda."

00:03:03.380 --> 00:03:06.096
Leo nipatapo maswali kuhusu 
jinsi nilivyofanikiwa kutoka,

00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:08.596
Natoa sababu moja wapo kubwa

00:03:08.620 --> 00:03:10.700
kuwa sikuwa na aibu kuomba msaada.

00:03:11.660 --> 00:03:14.276
Katika tabaka la hali ya kati 
au kaya tajiri,

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:16.076
kama mwanafunzi atakuwa na shida

00:03:16.100 --> 00:03:20.036
kuna uwezekano mkubwa kuwa 
mzazi au mwalimu atakuja kumsaidia

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:21.830
hata asipoomba msaada.

00:03:21.830 --> 00:03:24.186
Lakini, kama mtoto huyo 
amekulia katika umaskini

00:03:24.186 --> 00:03:25.420
na hataomba msaada,

00:03:26.060 --> 00:03:28.380
kuna uwezekano mkubwa 
hakuna atakayemsaidia.

00:03:28.700 --> 00:03:31.700
Hakuna wigo wa usalama wa kijamii 
unaopatikana.

00:03:32.910 --> 00:03:34.356
Kwa hiyo miaka saba iliyopita,

00:03:34.380 --> 00:03:37.196
Nilianza kuboresha 
mfumo wetu wa elimu ya umma

00:03:37.220 --> 00:03:39.820
nikichukua taswira 
ya mtazamo wangu wa moja kwa moja.

00:03:40.780 --> 00:03:42.352
Na nilianza na shule ya kiangazi.

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:47.116
Utafiti unatuambia kuwa 
theluthi mbili ya pengo la ufaulu,

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:49.476
ambayo 
ni tofauti katika upatikanaji wa elimu

00:03:49.500 --> 00:03:51.676
kati ya watoto matajiri na watoto maskini

00:03:51.700 --> 00:03:53.836
au watoto weusi na watoto weupe

00:03:53.860 --> 00:03:57.370
inaweza kuhusishwa moja kwa moja na 
upotevu wa elimu kipindi cha kiangazi

00:03:57.460 --> 00:04:00.276
Katika kaya maskini, 
watoto husahau karibu miezi mitatu

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.356
ya walichosoma kipindi cha mwaka wa shule

00:04:02.380 --> 00:04:03.716
wakati wa kiangazi.

00:04:03.740 --> 00:04:05.356
Wanarudi shule kipindi cha vuli,

00:04:05.380 --> 00:04:07.476
na walimu wao 
wanatumia miezi miwili mingine

00:04:07.476 --> 00:04:08.876
kurudia tena kuwafundisha.

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:10.396
Hiyo ni miezi mitano.

00:04:10.420 --> 00:04:13.036
Mwaka wa shule Marekani ni miezi 10 tu.

00:04:13.060 --> 00:04:15.676
Kama watoto watapoteza miezi 5 
ya kujifunza kila mwaka

00:04:15.700 --> 00:04:17.180
hiyo ni nusu ya elimu yao.

00:04:17.940 --> 00:04:19.140
Nusu.

00:04:19.900 --> 00:04:23.160
Kama watoto wangekuwa shule 
kipindi cha kiangazi, wasingerudi nyuma,

00:04:23.820 --> 00:04:26.420
lakini shule ya kiangazi iliyozoeleka 
imeundwa vibaya.

00:04:26.740 --> 00:04:28.796
Kwa watoto inaonekana kama adhabu,

00:04:28.820 --> 00:04:30.860
na kwa walimu inaonekana kama uyaya.

00:04:32.140 --> 00:04:36.156
Lakini tunatarajia vipi walimu wakuu 
kutekeleza programu madhubuti ya kiangazi

00:04:36.180 --> 00:04:38.636
ikiwa mwaka wa shule unaisha 
juma la mwisho la Juni

00:04:38.660 --> 00:04:41.040
na shule ya kiangazi inaanza 
juma moja tu baadaye?

00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:44.350
Yaani hakuna wakati wa kutosha 
kupata watu sahihi

00:04:44.350 --> 00:04:45.686
kuratibu ugavi,

00:04:45.686 --> 00:04:49.860
na kuunda mtaala mahsusi 
unaowavutia watoto na walimu.

00:04:51.580 --> 00:04:55.556
Lakini vipi kama tungetengeneza 
programu ya kiangazi

00:04:55.580 --> 00:04:59.276
ambayo ingewapa nguvu walimu 
kama makocha wa kufundisha

00:04:59.300 --> 00:05:01.300
kuendeleza waelimishaji watarajiwa?

00:05:02.540 --> 00:05:05.276
Vipi kama tungewawezesha 
wasomi wa chuo wa mfano

00:05:05.300 --> 00:05:06.580
kuwa wakufunzi wenza

00:05:07.380 --> 00:05:09.916
kuwasaidia watoto kutambua 
matarajio yao ya chuo?

00:05:09.940 --> 00:05:13.176
Vipi kama tungewawezesha 
watoto wenye ufaulu mkubwa kuwa washauri

00:05:13.176 --> 00:05:15.636
kuwafundisha vijana wenzao

00:05:15.660 --> 00:05:17.980
na kuwahamasisha 
kuwekeza katika elimu yao?

00:05:19.460 --> 00:05:23.196
Vipi kama tungewawezesha watoto wote 
kama wasomi,

00:05:23.220 --> 00:05:26.436
tukiwauliza ni vyuo gani 
wangependa kwenda,

00:05:26.460 --> 00:05:29.420
tukiunda shule ya kiangazi 
wanayotaka kwenda

00:05:30.220 --> 00:05:32.756
kuondoa kabisa upotevu wa elimu 
kipindi cha kiangazi

00:05:32.780 --> 00:05:34.980
na kufunga theluthi mbili 
ya pengo la ufaulu?

00:05:37.100 --> 00:05:41.716
Kiangazi hiki, timu yangu itakuwa imehudum
ia zaidi ya watoto 4,000 wa kaya maskini,

00:05:41.740 --> 00:05:44.676
imefundisha zaidi ya walimu watarajiwa 300

00:05:44.700 --> 00:05:46.996
na kuunda zaidi ya kazi 1,000 za msimu

00:05:47.020 --> 00:05:50.060
katika baadhi ya vitongoji vilivyo nyuma 
vya jiji la New York

00:05:50.820 --> 00:05:54.620
(Makofi na Vifijo)

00:05:56.660 --> 00:05:58.996
Na watoto wetu wanafanikiwa

00:05:59.020 --> 00:06:00.800
Miaka miwili ya uthamini binafsi

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:03.956
inatuambia kuwa watoto wetu 
wameondoa upotevu wa elimu wa kiangazi

00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:06.156
na wameongeza mwezi mmoja kwenye Hisabati

00:06:06.180 --> 00:06:07.630
na miezi miwili kwenye kusoma.

00:06:07.910 --> 00:06:11.516
Kwa hiyo badala ya kurudi shule kipindi 
cha vuli wakiwa miezi mitatu nyuma,

00:06:11.540 --> 00:06:14.410
sasa hivi wanarudi wakiwa 
miezi minne mbele kwenye Hisabati

00:06:15.380 --> 00:06:17.436
na miezi mitano mbele kwenye kusoma.

00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:20.860
(Makofi na Vifijo)

00:06:24.580 --> 00:06:26.516
Miaka 10 iliyopita, kama ungeniambia

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:30.716
kuwa ningehitimu katika 10% bora ya 
darasa langu kutoka taasisi ya Ivy League

00:06:30.740 --> 00:06:34.716
na kuwa na fursa ya kubadilisha japo 
kiduchu tu mfumo wetu wa elimu ya umma

00:06:34.740 --> 00:06:37.780
kwa kukabiliana na miezi miwili tu 
ya mwaka wa kalenda,

00:06:38.500 --> 00:06:40.236
ningesema,

00:06:40.260 --> 00:06:42.380
"Hapana, haiwezekani"

00:06:43.540 --> 00:06:45.036
Cha kusisimua ziaidi

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:48.236
ni kuwa kama tunaweza kuzuia 
miezi mitano ya upotevu wa muda

00:06:48.260 --> 00:06:50.220
kwa kuunda upya miezi miwili

00:06:51.300 --> 00:06:53.956
fikiria fursa tunazoweza kufumbua

00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:57.050
kwa kukabiliana na miezi yote iliyobaki 
ya mwaka wa kalenda

00:06:57.980 --> 00:06:59.196
Asanteni

00:06:59.220 --> 00:07:03.881
(Makofi na Vifijo)

